name: FNF Flippy Test | [Fliqpy]
description:
FNF Flippy Test

Here you can test another popular character from the Friday Night Funkin' series. Like other test games from here, you have some 'secret' keys and 5 different animations. Flippy or more correctly "Fliqpy" is a popular character from Happy Three Friends.

This FNF Test game with Flippy is with vocals and instrumental. You can play it from Pc, Windows, Linux or mobile, smartphone, tablet. Play FNF Flippy Test Online or Download the game.

If you are looking for fnf flippy test scratch, don't search anymore - you found something better!

Play FNF Flippy Online where you will find all the animations from the original mod created by miguel185. Here you will find one animation created by j0honnytest too.

What instrumental and skins can you find here?

  • Flippy Roll
  • Massacre
  • Flippin Out
  • UnFlipped Out
  • Hiding/Triggered

As you can see, here you can find all fnf flippy test songs. I've got information about this character from Fandom, one of the biggest sites when it comes to fnf flippy wiki.

Credits to j0nnytest and the team: https://gamebanana.com/wips/58270

Credits to miguel185 and the team: https://gamebanana.com/mods/300838

[!] This is not a demo of the actual game. This is just a character test game. [!]
